<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <title>Potvrzení o registraci</title>
    <style>
        body { font-family: DejaVu Sans, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; color: #333; }
        .header { margin-bottom: 30px; border-bottom: 2px solid #4a7c2c; padding-bottom: 10px; }
        .header table { width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; }
        .header img { height: 60px; width: auto; }
        .header h1 { color: #4a7c2c; margin: 0; font-size: 24px; text-align: right; }
        .content { margin-bottom: 30px; }
        .footer { text-align: center; font-size: 10px; color: #666; border-top: 1px solid #eee; padding-top: 10px; }
        table.details { width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; margin: 20px 0; }
        table.details th, table.details td { padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #eee; text-align: left; }
        table.details th { background-color: #f9f9f9; width: 150px; }
        .payment-info { background-color: #f9f9f9; padding: 20px; border-left: 4px solid #4a7c2c; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="header">
        <table>
            <tr>
                <td>
                    {if !empty($logoBase64)}
                        <img src="{$logoBase64|noescape}" alt="Logo">
                    {/if}
                </td>
                <td style="vertical-align: middle;">
                    <h1>Potvrzení o registraci</h1>
                </td>
            </tr>
        </table>
    </div>

    <div class="content">
        <p>Dobrý den,</p>
        <p>tímto potvrzujeme přijetí Vaší registrace do spolku <strong>{$SKP_NAME}</strong>.</p>

        <table class="details">
            <tr><th>Číslo člena</th><td>{$member->getMemberNumber()}</td></tr>
            <tr><th>Jméno a příjmení</th><td>{$member->getFullName()}</td></tr>
            <tr><th>Datum narození</th><td>{$member->getBirthDate() ? $member->getBirthDate('d.m.Y') : '-'}</td></tr>
            <tr><th>Email</th><td>{$member->email}</td></tr>
            <tr><th>Adresa</th><td>{$member->street}, {$member->zip} {$member->city}</td></tr>
        </table>

        <div class="payment-info">
            <h3>Informace k platbě</h3>
            <p>Uhraďte prosím registrační poplatek <strong>{$SKP_REGISTRATION_AMOUNT} Kč</strong> na účet do 14 dnů:</p>
            <p>
                <strong>Číslo účtu:</strong> {$SKP_ACCOUNT_NUMBER}<br>
                <strong>Variabilní symbol:</strong> {$member->getMemberNumber()}
            </p>
            {if !empty($qrBase64)}
                <div style="text-align: center; margin-top: 10px;">
                    <img src="{$qrBase64|noescape}" alt="QR platba" style="height: 150px; width: auto;">
                    <p style="font-size: 9px; color: #999;">QR platba</p>
                </div>
            {/if}
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="footer">
        <p>{$SKP_NAME} | IČO: {$SKP_ICO} | {$SKP_ADDRESS}</p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
